---
title: Oregano Chicken & Rosemary-Parmesan Fries with Garlic Aioli
description: This oregano chicken, marinated in yoghurt, is a simple combination that has been tried-and-tested and never fails to deliver a tender and flavoursome result. Served alongside the cheesy herb fries, this dish is sure to be a hit.
